Activity
public class Activity
extends LoggedAction.Default

This class generically represents any kind of activity done in the MEME system. Typically this is associated with a MolecularTransaction and/or a WorkLog object. This class is associated with activity_log in the MID. The identifier is the row_sequence the parent is the WorkLog associated with work_id The activity and detail fields are represeted as long and short descriptions. timestamp and authority are handled by the superclass. and there is one sub action, if the transaction_id is set.

Author:
MEME Group
